                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Iddings</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-07-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 3, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Iddings, chargé d’affaires, reports the receipt of the Department’s circular
                        telegram,<note n="1" xml:id="d454fn1">Printed, <ref target="#pg_312">p.
                            312</ref>.</note> of July 2, and compliance with its instructions.)</p>
            </div>
